high_descs: Turn to the right, then the left to face the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter, behind the bread.
Carry the plate and turn to the left, then the left again and face the sink on the right.
Place the plate in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the plate full of water.
Take the plate and turn to the right to locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the plate inside.
anns.task_desc: Fill a plate with water and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter with the loaf of bread on the left side.
Pick up the dirty bowl on the left back side of the counter.
Turn around, hang a right at the counter and turn left just before the white door to reach the sink ahead on your right.
Put the bowl inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk to the black fridge ahead.
Put the clean bowl inside the fridge on the top shelf to the left of the tomato and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bowl in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter in front of the loaf of bread.
Grab the green bowl off the counter.
Walk to the kitchen sink behind you.
Fill the bowl with water from the sink.
Walk to the fridge behind you.
Put the bowl of water in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Get a bowl and fill it with water to chill.
